address: Calle del Mondo Novo, 5801, 30122 Venezia VE, Italy
notes: Excellent flavor and consistency. A bit less structured than I typically prefer. Slightly heavy on the cocoa powder in the center, and the cream was lighter than I'd like, though these are subjective preferences, not technical faults. An amazing tiramisu.

This tiramisu is not traditional, nor a good execution. The tiramisu is colorful balloons representing Banksy's Girl with Balloon. I found the colors to be distracting and mess with the perceived flavor, texture and consistency was not appealing.
Large and exceptional Tiramisu. Consistency is perfect with excellent richness in the cream and balance with espresso.
Good flavor and texture on the ladyfingers, creams richness and consistency held it back from a higher score.
